{"tid":953911,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咖喱味屎定屎味咖喱","createTime":"2018-12-24T09:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T09:42:50.000Z","uid":228003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"486ebbf13d1ee3cb1629570ba7a6b931494d5e65","tid":953911,"uid":228003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"我響2年前識左A,好快就同佢變得好friend, friend到連佢失戀都係搵我呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大過左2-3個月, 我已經同佢挽到好埋, 甚至旁邊嘅人都以為我哋響埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 但其他人吾知我吔只係好好嘅朋友而已<br />\n不過過左1年, 我認識咗B, 但係A一直都好妥B, 當我同B挽嘅時候, 其實A係好不滿我同B一齊, 因為佢話B對佢做過啲好乞人憎嘅嘢, 但響我角度嚟睇其實係一件好小嘅事, 所以我叫佢洗咁care, 不過A話吾原諒B<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有同B講過呢件事, 佢吾係好記得佢做過啲咁嘅事, 因為真係好雞毛蒜皮嘅事, 但係A就因為咁樣blacklist咗B<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到咗近呢2個月, 我感覺上我同B仲friend過A, 而A要我響A同B之間揀一個, 點算好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4012a27407e757ef77a4e2f04d5608a0b4de35a7","tid":953911,"uid":228003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"sor for 1999"},{"pid":"543c5ee992078dbc309b1d846a9652b98265c653","tid":953911,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"挽你老母個爛臭閪"},{"pid":"ef4070b3370e2ab6b9e1df7dba5dce5ef2adae5e","tid":953911,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"挽你個死老母<br />\n留番啖氣去拜你老母山啦"}]}